data.description: Welcome to this exquisite newer-built home, where elegance & comfort intertwine seamlessly. Boasting a desirable location in a sought-after neighborhood, this home offers over 3200 square ft of modern living with its main level design, luxurious upgrades, and captivating landscape. This home features four bedrooms, three bathrooms, ensuring ample space for both relaxation and productivity. As you step inside, be prepared to be enchanted by the grandeur of over 9ft ceilings that enhance the spaciousness & natural light throughout. Every detail has been carefully considered, from the upgraded finishes to the harmonious blend of functionality & style. The open concept floor plan effortlessly combines the main living areas, providing a perfect setting for entertaining guests or spending quality time with loved ones. The gourmet kitchen is a true masterpiece, whether you're a seasoned chef or simply enjoy preparing meals, this kitchen will inspire your culinary creations. The adjacent dining area offers a warm ambiance, ideal for hosting intimate gatherings or larger dinner parties. Retreat to the luxurious primary suite, where relaxation and tranquility await. This private oasis features ample space, a spa-like ensuite bathroom, & a walk-in closet, ensuring a haven for rejuvenation. The 2nd main level bedroom/office offers a versatile space that can be tailored to your needs. The remarkable basement offers the perfect blend of functionality, luxury & comfort.  The basement offers a stunning great room with a cozy fireplace, wet bar for entrainment, storage room and two inviting bedrooms each with a walk-in closet. Step outside to discover a stunning landscape that creates an enchanting outdoor escape. The outdoor living spaces beckon you to relax and unwind on its the spacious extra large patio. Located in a desirable neighborhood, close to I25, shopping, restaurants this home offers the perfect balance of convenience and tranquility. Schedule your showing today!
